---
title: Pad See Ew with Mushrooms and Broccoli
description: In its native Thailand, pad see ew is always made to order and always in small quantities—never more than a few servings at a time. That’s not only so that it comes out sizzling and hot, but also so that all the ingredients have ample space to sear in the pan. Which is why this recipe is perfect for a quick dinner: as you’re tossing the rice noodles, soy sauce, veggies, and aromatics, you can pretend like you’re a Bangkok street-food hawker who’s whipping up a batch for a favorite customer.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w14-r10-e8e24f16.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w14-r10-94240499.pdf
cuisine: North America
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
